page_title: 'Quickstart: Use the OpenAI Service via the Python SDK'
page_description: Walkthrough on how to get started with Azure OpenAI and make your first completions call with the Python SDK.
chunk_content: Set upInstall the OpenAI Python client library with:# OpenAI Python 1.x```consolepip install openai```# OpenAI Python 0.28.1[!INCLUDE Deprecation]```consolepip install openai==0.28.1```---> [!NOTE]> This library is maintained by OpenAI. Refer to the release history to track the latest updates to the library.
